  <brief_title>Optimal Catheter Placement During Sonohysterography: Comparison of Cervical to Uterine Placement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Catheter Placement During Sonohysterography: A Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing Cervical to Uterine Placement</official_title>
  <sponsors>
